1997;;American Perfekt;;American;;Paul Chart;;Fairuza Balk, Robert Forster, Amanda Plummer;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/American_Perfekt;;Jake Nyman decides to take a professional vacation where all decisions will be made by the flip of a coin. He meets up with disenchanted Sandra Thomas, who becomes excited by the potential of having the coin make all the decisions. See, Flipism. Things seem okay, until Sandra vanishes and Alice becomes involved in Jake's life.